'''''Sonic the Hedgehog 3'''''{{Efn|Known in Japan as {{nihongo|'''''Sonic x Shadow TOKYO MISSION'''''|ソニック × シャドウ TOKYO MISSION|Sonikku x Shadō: Tokyo Mission|lead=yes|group=lower-alpha}}<ref name="AltTitle" />}} is a 2024 [[Action-adventure film|action-adventure]] [[comedy film]] based on the [[Sonic the Hedgehog|video game series]]. The third in the [[Sonic_the_Hedgehog_(film_series)#Films_2|''Sonic'' film series]], it was directed by [[Jeff Fowler]] and written by [[Patrick Casey (writer)|Pat Casey]], [[Josh Miller (filmmaker)|Josh Miller]], and [[John Whittington (screenwriter)|John Whittington]]. [[Jim Carrey]], [[Ben Schwartz]], [[Colleen O'Shaughnessey]], [[James Marsden]], [[Tika Sumpter]], and [[Idris Elba]] reprise their roles, with [[Keanu Reeves]] joining the cast. In the film, [[Sonic the Hedgehog (character)|Sonic]], [[Tails (Sonic the Hedgehog)|Tails]]  and [[Knuckles the Echidna|Knuckles]] face [[Shadow the Hedgehog]] (Reeves), who allies with the mad scientists [[Doctor Eggman|Ivo]] and [[Gerald Robotnik]] in pursuit of revenge against humanity.

''Sonic the Hedgehog 3'' was announced in February 2022 during [[Paramount Global|ViacomCBS]]'s investor event before the release of ''[[Sonic the Hedgehog 2 (film)|Sonic the Hedgehog 2]]'' (2022). Due to the [[2023 SAG-AFTRA strike]], filming for animated characters began in July 2023 in [[Surrey]], England, and filming with actors began that November in London. Production ended by March 2024. The plot draws elements from the video games ''[[Sonic Adventure 2]]'' (2001) and ''[[Shadow the Hedgehog (video game)|Shadow the Hedgehog]]'' (2005). Reeves was cast due to the parallels between his performance in the ''[[John Wick]]'' films and Fowler's vision for Shadow.

